# Web Architecture

- Nuxt 4 SPA: [apps/web/nuxt.config.ts](mdc:apps/web/nuxt.config.ts)
- Global layout and UI via `@nuxt/ui-pro`: [apps/web/app/layouts/default.vue](mdc:apps/web/app/layouts/default.vue)
- ORPC client and TanStack Query: [apps/web/app/plugins/orpc.ts](mdc:apps/web/app/plugins/orpc.ts)
  - Injected as `orpc` (query/mutation utils)
- Auth client: [apps/web/app/plugins/auth-client.ts](mdc:apps/web/app/plugins/auth-client.ts)
  - Injected as `authClient`
- Vue Query setup and toasts: [apps/web/app/plugins/vue-query.ts](mdc:apps/web/app/plugins/vue-query.ts)
- Local store wrapper: [apps/web/app/plugins/store.ts](mdc:apps/web/app/plugins/store.ts) / [apps/web/app/lib/store.ts](mdc:apps/web/app/lib/store.ts)

## Using RPC in components
- Access `const { orpc } = useNuxtApp()`; then call `orpc.<namespace>.<procedure>.useQuery(...)` or `.useMutation(...)` as provided by `@orpc/tanstack-query`.
- The base RPC URL comes from `runtimeConfig.public.serverURL` + `/rpc`.